---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Luke, Full-Stack Developer">
    <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <Navbar />
        <main class="flex-grow bg-yellow-200 py-8 sm:py-16 overflow-y-auto border-y-4 border-black">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 sm:p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-400 border-4 border-black transform rotate-12 translate-x-8 -translate-y-8"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-pink-400 border-4 border-black rounded-full -translate-x-10 translate-y-10"></div>

                    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-8 transform -rotate-1 break-words relative z-10">About Luke</h1>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-10">
                        <div class="bg-green-300 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Developer</h2>
                            <p>Full-stack developer with 10 years of experience, specializing in crafting robust web applications. Based in Wroc≈Çaw, Poland.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-blue-300 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1 md:col-span-2">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Journey</h2>
                            <p>My journey in tech began with curiosity about how things work. Today, I tackle complex problems with enthusiasm, turning them into elegant, efficient applications. I'm committed to continuous learning and sharing knowledge.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-yellow-300 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 md:col-span-2">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Approach</h2>
                            <p>As a seasoned developer, I've honed my skills in creating scalable, user-friendly solutions that drive business growth. My expertise spans from backend architecture to frontend design, ensuring seamless, end-to-end application development.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-purple-300 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform -rotate-1">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Geek</h2>
                            <p>In my free time, I embrace my inner geek. I'm an avid gamer, always ready for the next big release or a nostalgic replay of classics. This passion often influences my approach to creating engaging user experiences.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-pink-300 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transform rotate-1 md:col-span-3">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Person</h2>
                            <p>Beyond coding, I'm a proud husband and father. Our family, complete with a cat and a dog, keeps me grounded and inspired. We love exploring the beautiful landscapes of Poland together. Whether it's developing a cutting-edge application or spending quality time with my family, I approach life with enthusiasm and a dedication to excellence.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </div>
</Layout>